{"tid":461586,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（生果報）警隊證實警員跪地事件於昨日發","createTime":"2017-11-07T17:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T00:06:05.000Z","uid":29314,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d06a0266d96b72ac794003bb13e60c2fdda9a0","tid":461586,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:36:02.000Z","msg":"觀塘警署出現「奇警」，一名駐守觀塘警署的軍裝警員，早前疑因超時及假期補水問題曾與管理層有爭拗。後來他為求見指揮官回應，不時經常站在警署內的停車場空地，遙遙對著警區指揮官辦公室位置，站立不動，此舉引起同袍議論紛紛。近日該名警員將行動升級，不惜自製紙牌，寫上「SORRY SIR」字句，在停車場雙膝跪地拿起紙牌，似向指揮官辦公室「伸冤」，有同袍關注他的情況，特意上前了解，上述情景的相片卻被人拍下及放上網，引起市民議論紛紛。"},{"pid":"62999d3f2297d130fa3f14258ade358717d26d6d","tid":461586,"uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:37:27.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"http://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171107/large/15100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171107%2Flarge%2F15100&d=%2B8t1zD76Akrb5gSLLcVgApnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=bca11142\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171107/large/15100</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171107/large/1510034002_a745.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171107%2Flarge%2F1510034002_a745.jpg&h=30a997d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警員在觀塘警署停車場內高舉「SORRY SIR」紙牌跪地，引來公眾關注"},{"pid":"76062bec747957a247a9cd0e07af53f3d2e80bdc","tid":461586,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171107/large/1510034013_5be8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171107%2Flarge%2F1510034013_5be8.jpg&h=19460c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警員手持「SORRY SIR」紙牌跪地。有同袍上前了解"},{"pid":"89c3bd0cee953c7a15133db88ebdeecbcfee15ad","tid":461586,"uid":67686,"like":0,"dis